a factor of 2.

00:17:55.800 --> 00:17:59.210
So, once again, we see that
time and frequency scaling

00:17:59.210 --> 00:18:00.820
really works.

00:18:00.820 --> 00:18:05.340
Incidentally as Sandy pointed
out, and rightfully so, the

00:18:05.340 --> 00:18:10.200
